Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=12}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.19,0:02:10.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Borracha não conduz eletricidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:14.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Contra um homem de borracha,\Nos ataques de Enel são inúteis!
Comment: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:19.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He can defeat... Enel! -OG}Enel can... be defeated!{CB}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:17.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Enel...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:19.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,pode ser derrotado!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:37.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que diabos você é?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:40.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sou Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.60,0:02:43.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sou um pirata e um homem de borracha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:46.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Borracha?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:48.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É claro...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.44,0:02:51.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Borracha não existe\Nno White-White Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:54.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Relâmpago não funciona em mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:55.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Mantra.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:03.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:06.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:13.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:27.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:34.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não fique se achando.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:39.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Relâmpago pode fazer mais\Ndo que eletrocutar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:45.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se for ineficaz, eu ajusto\Nmeu estilo de luta de acordo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:50.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Me bater também não funciona!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:55.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:59.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então esse cara também prevê\Nmeus movimentos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.89,0:04:02.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que é essa tal "borracha"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:06.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não, espera um segundo...\NEle é apenas um paramecia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:10.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele deveria manter sua forma física\Nna maior parte do tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Lightning...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:13.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Forge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:21.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não tenho tempo pra brincar\Ncom alguém como você.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:25.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele está reformando a barra...\Nem uma lâmina?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:32.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pense nisso como relâmpago com forma!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:41.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Como eu imaginei,\Nvocê é fraco contra cortes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:41.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:45.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não admite isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:48.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:49.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)}Gatlin–
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:52.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele sumiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:54.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Atrás de você!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:01.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele está se movendo pelo ouro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:26.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ai, está quente!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.02,0:05:31.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Relâmpago não funciona, mas o calor\Ndesse tridente funciona direitinho, né?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:34.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.65,0:05:39.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Battle-Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:51.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Seu moleque insolente!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:56.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:09.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não é como se você tivesse ganhado mais braços!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.48,0:06:14.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:17.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Passeando numa sky island...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:21.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que timing terrível, homem do Mar Azul.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:27.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Lembre-se, eu sou Deus;\Neu faço o que quero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:31.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vou remodelar este mundo como eu bem entender!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:36.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um moleque do Mar Azul aparece aqui\Ne acha que pode arruinar meus planos?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:39.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que farsa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:48.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Agora, vamos assistir ao colapso\Ndesta nação juntos?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:53.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não me diga que...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:59.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Max 200 Milhões de Volts: Vari!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:15.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cavalo-Pássaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:18.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O navio está se movendo!\NO que a gente faz?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:27.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:33.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Contemplem! Ele se ergue!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:40.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A arca que vai me levar àquela\Nterra lendária, a Vearth Infinita...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:42.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maxim{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:51.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-Está subindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:08:00.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga, droga, droga, droga, droga...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:01.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Temos que escapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:05.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Rápido, derrota Enel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:07.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ahh! E-E-Espera um segundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:10.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se a gente derrotar Enel,\No navio não vai cair?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:13.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ahh, mas se não derrotarmos,\Na sky island vai ser destruída.
Comment: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:18.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And if we stay here...\Nwe'll be taken somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:16.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E se ficarmos aqui...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:18.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,vamos ser levados pra algum lugar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:25.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que a gente faz, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:37.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Para de entrar em pânico.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:40.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas... eu quero dizer...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:43.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você faz parte da tripulação do\Nfuturo Rei dos Piratas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:47.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Para de ficar com essa cara patética.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:55.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Rei dos Piratas?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:58.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E onde fica o reino dele?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:06.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele está acima de todos...\Ncomo o grande rei dos mares!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:12.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Impressionante.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:15.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então vamos resolver isso\Naqui mesmo no céu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:43.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Olha, Cavalo-Pássaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:45.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Parou!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:50.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Está preso na vearth\Ne não consegue subir mais!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:53.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas é só questão de tempo!\NEle está abrindo caminho!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.41,0:09:56.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não, vamos ficar pra trás!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:09:59.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos atrapalhar se formos!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.04,0:10:01.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy é um guerreiro do Mar Azul!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:05.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não devemos interferir\Nnum duelo de guerreiros!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:14.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}O circuito para o propósito final desta arca\Njá está em funcionamento.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.39,0:10:20.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Chama-se Deathpiea—o desespero encarnado\Ne a salvação deste mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:25.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que ele vai fazer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:46.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O-O que é aquilo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:50.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Chefe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:53.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Alguma coisa está errada com\No céu acima de Upper Yard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:55.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O céu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.43,0:10:58.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É, escureceu de repente.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.68,0:11:02.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É a primeira vez que eu vejo\No céu de Skypiea assim!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:04.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É assustador.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:07.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Algo aconteceu com os guerreiros?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:14.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ver nuvens tão espessas no\Ncéu do White-White Sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.99,0:11:18.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É isso mesmo! São nuvens de trovão.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:24.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Usando minha energia, Deathpiea\Ndescarrega nuvens de trovão
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:26.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,com correntes extremamente turbulentas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:27.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nuvens de trovão?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:32.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Em breve, as nuvens vão\Nacumular energia suficiente
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:35.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,pra cobrir toda Skypiea de escuridão.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:40.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sob meu comando, dezenas de\Nrelâmpagos vão chover,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.89,0:11:44.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,aniquilando o país inteiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.73,0:11:48.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Permitam-me demonstrar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:01.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Está vindo de Upper Yard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:03.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Rápido para os navios!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,0:12:08.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mantenham a calma e não entrem em pânico!\NVão para o Cloud End!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.05,0:12:15.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Como ousa, Enel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.14,0:12:24.14,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Enel...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:35.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que você acabou de...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:40.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu provoquei os anjos um pouco.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:43.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você acha que um deus pode\Nse livrar de tudo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:44.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:47.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vidas, terras, tudo o que eu quiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:51.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E isso inclui você!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:53.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Os preparativos para a festa\Njá começaram!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:02.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A-Ai! Ai, ai, ai, ai...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essa é uma lança de alta voltagem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:17.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quente!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:27.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:32.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não tem algum jeito de eu contra-atacar\Nessa coisa de prever movimentos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:35.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Já sei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:40.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.01,0:13:40.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Daze...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:44.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que diabos você está fazendo, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:59.53,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele está desviando dos ataques\Npor puro instinto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.53,0:14:04.49,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Não, ele é como grama,\Napenas balançando com o vento.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:08.20,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,A mente dele está vazia,\Nentão Enel não consegue ler!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:16.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quando eu estou aéreo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:20.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,eu também não consigo atacar!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:21.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Seu idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:25.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se eu conseguisse agarrá-lo de algum jeito,\Neu poderia equilibrar as coisas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:27.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Já sei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:35.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum Octopus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:37.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Chega!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:39.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Chega de ideias malucas!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:43.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Parece que mantra não é do seu agrado.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:44.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Era de se esperar!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:48.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Afinal, é mais uma\Nmarca da minha supremacia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:50.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ali deve funcionar!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:54.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:56.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não importa o que você faça,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:59.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,você é só um idiota que calhou\Nde ser imune a relâmpago!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:01.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}...Octopus...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:04.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê? Ele está mirando no navio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:06.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}...Fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:12.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Imbecil!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:13.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você não consegue me acertar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:16.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Está tentando destruir\No navio?! Que inútil!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:43.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É claro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:45.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estão ricocheteando!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:48.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy não está controlando os socos\Nque ricocheteiam da parede!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:51.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu não vou mais deixar você fugir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:54.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:56.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-Espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:58.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}...Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:16.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:17.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele está vindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:21.46,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu... Eu preciso escapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:25.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:26.84,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Aí vem!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:32.22,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu... Eu preciso me esquivar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:35.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}...Rifle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:07.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O navio está saindo da vearth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:11.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah não! O que a gente faz?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.18,0:17:13.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O navio vai voar embora!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:16.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você conseguiu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:17.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você conseguiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:20.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,M-Mas o navio...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:21.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Está voando embora!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:24.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:26.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mesmo depois de tudo isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:31.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Seus tolos! I-Isso é tudo que vocês têm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:41.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quando eu me livrar de vocês,\No mundo será meu novamente!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:50.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu serei temido, adorado\Ne reverenciado por todos mais uma vez.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:52.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esse é o meu mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:57.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vermes como vocês não são páreo pra mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.35,0:18:03.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pra mim... nada é impossível!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:11.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sou o Deus todo-poderoso!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:13.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Corram!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:20.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Olhem! Alguma coisa está flutuando\Nno céu acima de Upper Yard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:22.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,U-Um navio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:26.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser! Um navio voador...\NEu nunca ouvi falar de tal coisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:36.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É aquele navio que está\Ndeixando o céu escuro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.35,0:18:38.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Deus deve estar naquele navio!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.31,0:18:41.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:43.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Rápido! Corram!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.69,0:18:46.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Embarquem nos navios!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.36,0:18:54.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Muitos navios estão saindo de Angel Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:19:01.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo? De onde\Nvieram essas nuvens escuras?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:04.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hm? Alguém está vindo pra cá!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.00,0:19:07.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, Shandianos!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:10.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vocês deviam preparar\Nseus navios imediatamente também!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:13.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não há mais esperança\Npra este país!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:14.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.01,0:19:16.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fujam!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.39,0:19:17.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pro Mar Azul!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:20.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,P-Pro Mar Azul?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:28.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um navio...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:32.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Deus... Enel...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:38.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Testemunhe, homem de borracha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:42.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,o desespero de uma ilha em queda.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:48.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A sky island acabou.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:52.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,As vidas dos anjos serão extintas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:54.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ninguém pode parar isso agora...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.68,0:19:58.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,nem mesmo você!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:19:59.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Para com isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:01.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Lightning...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:03.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O muro de ouro...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:04.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ora, seu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:06.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}...Forge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:07.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Q-Quente!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:10.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele derreteu com eletricidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:13.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga, está queimando!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:16.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:21.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não sai! Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:23.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Homem de borracha do Mar Azul...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:28.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que eu deveria sujar\Nminhas mãos lutando com você?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:31.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tira isso, seu desgraçado!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:35.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Afinal, eu não aguento\Nlevar mais um soco seu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:39.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então, por que não...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:43.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,nos separamos aqui e agora?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:46.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Em honra ao seu esforço valente,\Neu lhe concedo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.77,0:20:49.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,este ouro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.71,0:21:10.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:16.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Com você fora do caminho,\No mundo será meu mais uma vez.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.72,0:21:23.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não haverá ninguém\Nno mundo que possa me derrotar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:26.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,"No mundo"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.73,0:21:30.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você é burro ou o quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:32.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Muita gente pode!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:37.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,De onde a gente vem, tem\Nmonstros por todo lado!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.61,0:21:39.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Comparado a eles...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:44.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você é um moleque barulhento, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:47.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Caia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.49,0:21:49.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Junto com a sky island!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:52.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você é apenas um...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:53.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,N-Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.50,0:21:57.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.26,0:22:05.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:08.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Maldito!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.47,0:22:11.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É o Luffy, Cavalo-Pássaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:13.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O Luffy está caindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:19.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É... Aisa e Pierre!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.57,0:22:21.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então era isso...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.53,0:22:25.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,aquele sussurro furtivo que eu estava ouvindo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.03,0:22:31.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Lute comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.54,0:22:33.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Estamos indo te salvar!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.29,0:22:36.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que irritante!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.67,0:22:39.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Apenas aceite seu destino!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.05,0:22:41.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aisa! Pierre! Cuidado! Desviem!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.13,0:22:45.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Enel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.64,0:22:48.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Castigo de Deus:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.06,0:22:51.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}El Thor!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.24,0:23:06.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.49,0:23:11.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aisa! Pierre!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:15.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso me custou, mesmo pra mim.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.83,0:23:18.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Porém... esta é a conclusão.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.47,0:23:31.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que navio grande...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:35.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então é essa a arca que\Nos Sacerdotes foram forçados a construir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:43.32,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Aqui, o nordeste da ilha.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.32,0:23:47.66,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Depois de pegarem o ouro,\Na gente se encontra nessa praia.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.11,0:23:51.62,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Então quando todo mundo estiver lá,\Nvocês vão embora?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.62,0:23:55.91,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu me contentava só com o tesouro,\Nse quer saber a verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.04,0:23:59.29,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,– N... Nami...\N– N... Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.92,0:24:04.26,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Eles estão voltando pro navio deles...\Nna praia nordeste.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.26,0:24:07.51,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Vou pra lá... e esperar\Ntodo mundo chegar.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.51,0:24:10.18,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Preciso ajudá-los\Na voltar pro Mar Azul!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.76,0:24:14.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sou a única que pode mostrar a eles\Ncomo sair desta sky island!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.48,0:24:19.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Preciso ir logo pro {\i1}Going Merry{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.82,0:24:23.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah, Nami querida...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.82,0:24:26.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hm... O que foi?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.66,0:24:29.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.87,0:24:34.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu quero ficar no sonho\Ncom minha doce Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.16,0:24:35.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hm...? Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.25,0:24:37.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.29,0:24:44.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Q-Que diabos é aquilo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.51,0:24:47.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mellorine... Mellorine, Mellorine...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.59,0:24:50.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mellorine, Mellorine,\NMellorine, Mellorine, Mello–{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.97,0:24:52.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.14,0:24:54.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que diabos...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.14,0:25:00.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei! Acorda, idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.02,0:25:02.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não é hora de ficar deitado!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.27,0:25:06.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que foi...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.15,0:25:07.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hã? Eu estava...!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.82,0:25:09.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cala a boca e se prepara!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.45,0:25:12.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hã? Me preparar?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.57,0:25:14.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos resgatar a Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.83,0:25:16.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Resgatar?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.54,0:25:17.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Res–
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.66,0:25:22.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É mesmo! Agora eu lembrei!\NDeus! Deus apareceu!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.18,0:25:37.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah, não...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.72,0:25:40.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Deus, Deus, Deus, Deus...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.06,0:25:40.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele não está mais aqui!\NJá foi embora há muito tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.14,0:25:45.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tremendo, tremendo, tremendo,\Natrapalhando, atrapalhando, atrapalhando...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.06,0:25:45.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Foi ele quem sequestrou a Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.32,0:25:46.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,S-Sequestrou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.19,0:25:51.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga! É nossa culpa ela ter sido levada!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.82,0:25:53.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É porque ela é tão linda!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.78,0:25:55.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sequestrada, é...?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.20,0:25:58.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pra onde ele a levou?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.92,0:26:02.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Lá em cima!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.13,0:26:05.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.29,0:26:09.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que é aquilo?! Um navio...?!\NNa floresta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.34,0:26:12.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Foi breve, mas eu vi\Num relance dela.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.68,0:26:15.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A Nami está naquele navio.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.97,0:26:19.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não importa o que aquela coisa é!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.10,0:26:22.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que importa é que a camiseta dela saiu.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.23,0:26:24.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso {\\i1}definitivamente{\\i0} não importa!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.56,0:26:28.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu não entendo nada disso.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.36,0:26:30.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cadê a Conis? Ou o cavaleiro estranho?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.28,0:26:34.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu também não entendo,\Nmas temos que nos apressar!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.87,0:26:45.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, pra onde estamos indo, Sanji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.88,0:26:48.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pra onde mais?! Aquele navio!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.09,0:26:49.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O-O-O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.59,0:26:52.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se esperarmos mais,\Nnão vamos conseguir embarcar!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.92,0:26:53.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É agora ou nunca!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.80,0:26:57.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hm, e eu por acaso\Ntambém estaria indo, estaria?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.60,0:26:58.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É claro que sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.68,0:27:01.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você tem aquela coisa,\Nnão tem?! A corda de barriga?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.72,0:27:03.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah, você quer dizer o "Usopp Aah-eeh-ah"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.85,0:27:06.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu empresto pra você,\Ne eu posso ficar aqu–
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.23,0:27:07.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Anda logo!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.48,0:27:08.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu não quero! E-Espera um pouco!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.90,0:27:12.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Idiota! Não há tempo a perder!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.32,0:27:18.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estou indo te buscar,\Nminha doce Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.62,0:27:25.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Agora que a {\\i1}Arca Maxim{\\i0}\Nfoi ativada,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.50,0:27:29.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,nenhuma quantidade de choro ou grito\Npode salvar este país.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.92,0:27:34.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que foi? Seja grata\Npor ter sobrevivido até aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.67,0:27:36.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não pense nos fracos.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.39,0:27:40.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Deve haver um futuro\Nque você deseja, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.18,0:27:42.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um futuro que eu desejo...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.47,0:27:44.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim, tem um.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.35,0:27:51.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas se eu for com você,\Nnão vai ser diferente de estar sozinha.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.53,0:27:57.53,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos começar a festa!\NÉ a véspera do festival de caça ao ouro!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.53,0:27:59.99,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos pegar o tesouro!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.99,0:28:02.62,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,– Ouro!\N– Ouro!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.96,0:28:12.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Qual a graça de conseguir\No que você quer sozinho?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.55,0:28:18.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sinceramente, tem muita coisa que\Neu quero e tanto que eu adoraria fazer...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.01,0:28:21.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,mas se eu tenho que abandonar minha tripulação\Ne ir com você no lugar...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.47,0:28:27.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,então eu não quero mais nada!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.94,0:28:31.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você não quer nada?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.07,0:28:41.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso inclui a sua vida, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.79,0:28:46.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.00,0:28:47.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, Suu?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.29,0:28:55.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nem o Usopp nem o Sanji\Nestavam em condições de se mover!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.84,0:28:57.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.34,0:29:00.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que eles não estão aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.34,0:29:02.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pra onde eles foram?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.39,0:29:08.64,Main-207-,,0,0,21,,O Sanji acordou...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.64,0:29:11.35,Main-207-,,0,0,21,,e fez o Usopp levantar também.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.35,0:29:13.61,Main-207-,,0,0,21,,Aí os dois correram...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.61,0:29:15.57,Main-207-,,0,0,21,,e pularam... direto pra cima?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.19,0:29:19.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?! Não me diga que...!\NEles foram pra aquele navio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.12,0:29:24.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O corpo deles ainda não...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.62,0:29:28.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que imprudência!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.56,0:29:55.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Usopp Aah-eeh-ah-eeh...\Nespera! Ah-eeh...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.77,0:30:00.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Deus ou não, se ele encostar\Num dedo na Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.15,0:30:04.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,eu vou virar o demônio do Mar Azul!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.91,0:30:10.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.21,0:30:18.63,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.63,0:30:20.92,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Vou tomar emprestada sua determinação!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=13}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=14}============================SIGNS AND TITLE=========================
